description: Margaret`s maidservant, wholly devoted to caring for her "miss". Elenore`s family has served Burtons for generations, so she considers it her duty to protect absent-minded and clumsy Margaret from anything remotely dangerous - to the point of researching all her classmates` backgrounds. Her devotion and persistence helped her to graduate from school years ahead of the rest and later, become an expert in hand to hand combat.
name: Elenore Baker
